        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Canva Pro costs $13 per month when billed monthly, or $10 per month when billed annually ($120/year). It includes 100M+ premium stock assets, 1TB storage, full Magic Studio AI features (AI image generation, Magic Eraser, Magic Write, Magic Morph, Magic Expand), Brand Kits, background removal, and transparent background export.</p>
